sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Shopper
  participant Store as Storefront
  participant Cart as Cart Service
  participant Pay as Payment Gateway
  participant OMS as Order Service

  Shopper->>Store: Click "Checkout"
  Store->>Cart: Get current cart
  Cart-->>Store: Cart items + totals
  Store->>Pay: Authorize payment
  Pay-->>Store: Payment approved
  Store->>OMS: Create order
  OMS-->>Store: Order confirmation
  Store-->>Shopper: Show thank-you page
